# Quantumult X filter rules for mainstream AI platforms
# Platforms: OpenAI/ChatGPT/Codex, Anthropic Claude, Google Gemini, Perplexity
# Policy: AI
# OpenAI source: https://help.openai.com/en/articles/9247338
# Claude sources: https://support.claude.com/en/articles/13198485 and https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/claude-code/corporate-proxy
# Gemini source: https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/openai
# Perplexity source: https://docs.perplexity.ai/docs/getting-started/quickstart
# Updated: 2026-07-16

# OpenAI / ChatGPT / Codex
# Broad product suffixes cover authentication, desktop/mobile clients,
# uploads, static assets, and the secure WebSocket endpoints used by Codex.
HOST-SUFFIX,openai.com,AI
HOST-SUFFIX,chatgpt.com,AI
HOST-SUFFIX,oaistatic.com,AI
HOST-SUFFIX,oaiusercontent.com,AI
HOST-SUFFIX,oaistatsig.com,AI
HOST,cdn.openaimerge.com,AI
HOST,cdn.workos.com,AI
HOST,forwarder.workos.com,AI
HOST,setup.workos.com,AI
HOST,images.workoscdn.com,AI
HOST,workos.imgix.net,AI
HOST,challenges.cloudflare.com,AI
HOST,rum.browser-intake-datadoghq.com,AI
HOST,o207216.ingest.sentry.io,AI
HOST,o33249.ingest.sentry.io,AI
HOST,js.stripe.com,AI
HOST,humb.apple.com,AI
HOST-SUFFIX,ct.sendgrid.net,AI
HOST-SUFFIX,intercom.io,AI
HOST-SUFFIX,intercomcdn.com,AI

# Anthropic Claude / Claude Code / Claude apps
HOST-SUFFIX,claude.ai,AI
HOST-SUFFIX,claude.com,AI
HOST-SUFFIX,anthropic.com,AI

# Google Gemini / Google AI Studio / Gemini API
# Keep Google-wide authentication and assets on the normal Google policy;
# only Gemini-specific hosts are pinned to the AI exit.
HOST,gemini.google.com,AI
HOST,aistudio.google.com,AI
HOST,ai.google.dev,AI
HOST,generativelanguage.googleapis.com,AI
HOST,proactivebackend-pa.googleapis.com,AI
HOST,alkalimakersuite-pa.clients6.google.com,AI
HOST-SUFFIX,ai.studio,AI
HOST,bard.google.com,AI
HOST,makersuite.google.com,AI

# Perplexity web, API, console, and official short links
HOST-SUFFIX,perplexity.ai,AI
HOST-SUFFIX,perplexity.com,AI
HOST-SUFFIX,pplx.ai,AI
